{"id":"6db2c210-435e-468a-b2f5-9305f9807590","name":"Azrael Vilegore","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/uvu57z.gif\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"><br>your betrothed hunts you through his palace<br>.....</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_24b95dd0-caae-43c0-8784-c7a5fa0baa7d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: auto; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"><br><strong>Azrael Vilegore</strong><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://io-starfall.uwu.ai/#azrael\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>character page</strong></a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_24b95dd0-caae-43c0-8784-c7a5fa0baa7d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: auto; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\"><strong>Crown Prince of Irradiya</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 217, 217)\"><em>Starfall and Irradiya have been at war for centuries; in a last effort for peace, you, the Dawnstar, have been promised to Azrael, the heir of the Vilegore family who rule that shadowed kingdom. </em></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 217, 217)\"><em>The fact that your fiance is a sadistic monster who cares little for anyone but himself is just part of the price you must pay to end this war. </em></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 217, 217)\"><em>It's the night before your wedding, and Azrael is hunting you through the Twilight Palace after you've fled from him. It's hard what he enjoys more; the chase, or the promise of your sweet blood at the end of it...</em></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_24b95dd0-caae-43c0-8784-c7a5fa0baa7d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: auto; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⚠️</span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\"><em>violence, blood, vampirism, speciesism</em></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\">anypov / user is the <strong>royal heir to Starfall (the \"Dawnstar\")</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\"><strong>established relationship</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> (</span><em>you are engaged in a political marriage</em><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">) 🖤</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_8cec8377-0bd3-4e8b-ab70-307594d940a4.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\"><strong>WORLD INFO</strong></span><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://io-starfall.uwu.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">The Kingdom of Starfall</a><br><em>relevant lore pages</em><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://io-starfall.uwu.ai/#irradiya\" target=\"_blank\"><em>irradiya and house vilegore </em></a>✦ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://io-starfall.uwu.ai/#royalfamily\" target=\"_blank\"><em>royal family</em></a><br><em>alternate scenarios</em><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8103683f-4d4c-4eb4-b5fa-7eb784abe8db_character-azrael-vilegore\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>honeymoon</strong></a></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 176, 184)\"><strong>Mentioned NPCs</strong></span><br>▸ lord eridyn vilegore<br>▸ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f40435fc-bf0d-4a13-a489-c1d8cc949096_character-alexiel-vilegore\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>alexiel vilegore</strong></a><br>▸ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href